          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1628678666771-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>curried cauliflower</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) and put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>in the oven for 15-20 min or until tender</p><p>Once the cauliflower is almost cooked, add the <strong>cashew nuts </strong>and <strong>cauliflower leaves </strong>to the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> and return it to the oven for 3-4 min further or until the nuts are toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch the nuts like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
